    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) is accepted given the standardized regulatory nature of the ASTM F1717 protocol and the consistency of results across two independent laboratories. All three QoIs fall within the 10% acceptance bound and E/uval < 1.96. The FEA framework is deemed sufficiently credible to support the regulatory submission decision.",
